-111_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Before we delve deeper, let's demystify cholesterol. It's a waxy substance found in the blood, essential for building cells and producing hormones. However, too much LDL (low-density lipoprotein) cholesterol, often termed "bad" cholesterol, can accumulate in the arteries, leading to blockages and increasing the risk of heart disease. On the other hand, HDL (high-density lipoprotein) cholesterol is known as "good" cholesterol, as it helps remove LDL cholesterol from the bloodstream.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-113_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-114_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-115_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_1b72cc55-5fd2-4489-9465-f5e259e73d4e.jpg?v=1709723070" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_1b72cc55-5fd2-4489-9465-f5e259e73d4e.jpg?v=1709723070 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Unlocking Wellness: Cholesterol Screening and Solutions - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Unlocking Wellness: Cholesterol Screening and Solutions - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-117_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-118_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mohdizzuanbinroslan via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-120_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-121_ pf-text-1">Cardiovascular diseases (CVDs) are the leading cause of death globally, with high cholesterol being a significant risk factor.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-123_ pf-text-1">In the UK alone, about 7 million people are living with heart or circulatory diseases.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-125_ pf-text-1">According to the World Health Organisation (WHO), raised cholesterol increases the risk of heart disease and stroke.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-127_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-128_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-129_ pf-heading-1-h3">The importance of National Cholesterol Month</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/small-black-circle-with-the-word-awareness-the-co-2023-11-27-05-33-59-utc_2.jpg?v=1709741749" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/small-black-circle-with-the-word-awareness-the-co-2023-11-27-05-33-59-utc_2.jpg?v=1709741749 1536w" width="1000" height="666" alt="Unlocking Wellness: Cholesterol Screening and Solutions - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Unlocking Wellness: Cholesterol Screening and Solutions - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-131_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-132_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by fauziEv8 via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-134_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-135_ pf-text-1"><b>Education and awareness</b> - National Cholesterol Month serves as a beacon of knowledge, illuminating the pathways to heart health. Organisations like Heart UK, the British Heart Foundation, and The Mandatory Training Group tirelessly work to raise awareness through educational campaigns, screenings, and community events. By empowering individuals with knowledge about cholesterol and its management, we pave the way for healthier hearts across the nation.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-137_ pf-text-1"><b>Collaboration and support</b> - Collaboration among global health organisations such as the World Heart Federation, National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute (NHLBI), and European Atherosclerosis Society amplifies the impact of National Cholesterol Month. These organisations provide resources, support research, and advocate for policies aimed at reducing the burden of cardiovascular diseases worldwide.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-139_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-140_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-141_ pf-heading-1-h3">Recommendations for better heart health</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/front-view-different-pills-with-orange-slice-on-li-2023-11-27-05-25-47-utc_1.jpg?v=1709741863" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/front-view-different-pills-with-orange-slice-on-li-2023-11-27-05-25-47-utc_1.jpg?v=1709741863 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="The Symphony of Heart Health: A Guide to National Cholesterol Month - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="The Symphony of Heart Health: A Guide to National Cholesterol Month - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-143_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-144_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by AydinovKamran via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spa